  m_text: "Wintertime in Finland is tough, but not for a seasoned Finn like you.
    Quite the opposite, this is the prime time for ice fishing, an important part
    of your routine. Trudging out of the m\xF6kki, gear in hand, you are ready to
    drill a hole in the lake, sit down and enjoy some quality time fishing in the
    wilderness."
