  m_text: "You find out your grandma is coming with your parents to the m\xF6kki.
    You desperately want to impress her with your baking skills, so you decide to
    make not one, but two pies, a mushroom one and a mixed berry one. In traditional
    young adult fashion, you have neither. Oh well, no better opportunity than this
    one to go foraging in the forest!"
